Make all scripts executable:

chmod +x networking/*.sh system_updates/*.sh servers/*.sh security/*.sh ldap/*.sh


Push the folder structure to GitHub:

git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit: Linux Networking, Servers, System Update commands"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/yourusername/Linux-Networking-Servers.git
git push -u origin main
